      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Affordable project or parts car for someone handy and realistic about what it needs. This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant repairs and sorting before it\u2019s ready for dependable road use, but it could still be a worthwhile starting point for the right buyer. Priced fairly for its condition and best suited for a buyer looking for a fixer-upper rather than a turn-key driver.",
