    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition example that presents well overall and should make a solid driver for the next owner. It runs and drives as it should, with a well-kept appearance inside and out, though it is not a flawless show car and should be expected to have some normal age-related wear, small blemishes, and minor signs of use. The interior appears cared for, the exterior shows nicely, and overall it gives the impression of a car that has been maintained rather than neglected. A good fit for someone looking for a nice, usable example they can enjoy right away without paying mint-condition money.",
      "price": 33900.0,
