    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a budget-minded buyer, commuter, or project shopper. It shows its age and condition, but it remains a practical opportunity for someone seeking dependable basic transportation at a low cost. A straightforward value buy with plenty of potential for the right owner.",
