      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a first project, or a parts car with plenty to offer. It has the kind of honest, well-used character you\u2019d expect, and for the right buyer, there\u2019s real value here. If you\u2019re handy, practical, or just want something inexpensive to work with, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with classic, no-nonsense mechanical character. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels usable, and it has the kind of straightforward, serviceable setup that makes a great project, commuter, or weekend fixer-upper. It shows cosmetic age and needs attention in places, but the fundamentals are there for someone who appreciates a car with real potential instead of overpolished hype. Priced to move for a buyer who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
