      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its panels and plenty of life left for the right driver. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly ride with personality, whether you need a practical runabout, a weekend project, or a dependable set of wheels to make your own. There\u2019s a certain gritty charm here: turn the key, imagine the possibilities, and see the value in a vehicle that still has plenty to give.",
      "price": 6800.0,
